#: ../../language/error_codes/E4151.md:1
msgid "E4151"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4151.md:3
msgid ""
"Values of type `FuncRef[T]` must be closed function -- it should not capture"
" any local variables."
msgstr "`FuncRef[T]` 类型的值必须是闭合函数——它不应该捕获任何局部变量。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4151.md:5
msgid ""
"MoonBit provides a builtin type `FuncRef[T]`, which represents closed "
"function of type `T`. In MoonBit's native backend, `FuncRef[T]` corresponds "
"to function pointer type, so `FuncRef[T]` can be passed to C FFI functions "
"requiring a callback directly, for example setting UNIX signal handler. "
"Values of type `FuncRef[T]` must be closed function type, if a function "
"which captures free variables or a non-function is supplied, an error will "
"be reported."
msgstr ""
"MoonBit 提供了一个内建类型 `FuncRef[T]`，用于表示类型为 `T` 的无捕获的函数。在 MoonBit "
"的原生后端，`FuncRef[T]` 直接对应函数指针类型，因此 `FuncRef[T]` 可以作为回调函数直接被传递给 C FFI，例如 UNIX "
"的信号处理回调。`FuncRef[T]` 类型的值必须是无捕获的函数，因此如果提供了一个有捕获的函数或一个非函数的值，编译器就会产生本错误。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4151.md:11
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4151.md:12
msgid ""
"test {\n"
"  let x : Int = 42\n"
"  let _ : FuncRef[() -> Unit] = fn () { println(x) }\n"
"}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4151.md:16
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4151.md:17
msgid ""
"If your callback function really needs to have captures, consider adding the"
" captures as extra parameters to the function."
msgstr "如果您的回调函数真的需要捕获局部变量，可以把局部变量变成回调函数的额外参数。"

